    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they're already so stressed. every time they come over, they look so tired. i see them checking their watches. if i just... stepped aside, they could finally get back to their own lives without this constant worry about me. wouldn't a clean break be more peaceful for everyone than this slow decline?",
